$interpreted: Lizard General: ...The number of refugees has far exceeded our estimations. We've also observed more and more monsters making their way south from the East...
Diana: I see. But with some rearrangement of our border troops—
Diana: General!? What are you...
Lizard General: On behalf of the Desert Kingdom, we must beseech Your Majesty!
Diana: On behalf of the Desert Kingdom?
Lizard General: As Your Majesty must already know, our men have reached their limit. Please, Your Majesty, put our Kingdom's safety above all else!
Diana: ......
Lizard General: ...Please, forgive your humble servant for earnestly requesting... that the refugees be turned away!
Diana: ...So, has it come to this already?
Diana: The Sun Queen did warn me. I hoped to hold out a little longer, to save as many as I could...
Lizard General: ...Do you not reproach us for our defiance, Your Majesty?
Diana: I've asked too much of you. Thank you for sticking with me all this time.
Diana: ...I hereby decree that the ports be closed off, effective immediately!
Lizard Soldier: All your papers seem to be in order... You may go.
Lizard Soldier: Chop chop, the Queen's ordered the port shut. You lot are the last travellers allowed through.
Hestia: Thank you!
Nigel: —Wait!
Nigel: ...There's even monsters here, too. I don't know what the situation in Atlas is... Yamitsuki and the rest...
Izumi: I can't speak for Yamitsuki, but I do know they'll close the city gates if we don't hurry~
Lizard Soldier: Halt! By royal decree, the desert ports have been shut! I cannot let you through!
Nigel: Our ship was ambushed by monsters and thrown off course.
Nigel: We'll be monster kibble if we hang around here any longer. You're inhuman!!
Nigel: You're...
Lizard Soldier: I wish I could help. But you have only your rotten luck to blame.
Izumi: Ooowwww~ What'll we do, Nigel?
Izumi: I told you we'd never make it back to Atlas. We should have stayed in the East to see how things would play out~
Nigel: ...And I told you to shut your trap.
Izumi: Oowww touché~
Izumi: Hmm, let me think~ I don't think we'll be able to wipe out an entire nation...
Izumi: But the two of us could still slaughter everybody here! They won't allow us in, and I'm getting bored out here~
Nigel: ......
Nigel: ...What are you talking about, you imbecile. The Desert Kingdom would take revenge on Atlas if we were to do such a thing.
Izumi: Ehh? That's too bad, I was looking forward to it~
Izumi: You've turned into such a bore since you took charge, Nigel.
Nigel: If we can't get in, we have to at least let Yamitsuki know where we are... There must be a way...
Nigel: Weren't you on the ship earlier...
Puggi: Huh? Who are you, now? I've got no interest in dudes...
